  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bb1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Basil also fled the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Sri Lankan Finance Minister Basil Rajapaksa has left Sri Lanka and traveled to the United States, BBC reported.",
        "This will end the Rajapaksa rule in Sri Lanka for decades, according to the BBC.",
        "Officials of the Immigration and Emigration Department said on Tuesday (12) that officials on duty at Katunayake and Mattala International Airport VIP Service have decided to step down from their duties to prevent indicted former political figures from fleeing the country.",
        "The officers were off duty when Basil Rajapaksa was about to leave the country through the silk route gate used by prominent figures at the Katunayake Bandaranaike International Airport.",
        "The officials of the Department of Immigration and Emigration announced on Tuesday (12) evening that they had received information that Basil Rajapaksa was planning to leave the country through the Mattala Airport and that he was withdrawing from the airport's service.",
        "However, according to reports, authorities cannot bar the travel of a US citizen because of Basil, who is a dual citizen and holds a US passport.",
        "It is reported that Basil may have been given permission to leave the country based on that."
      ],
